    </div>

    <div class="caveat"><strong>This tool is a guide only. Results may not account for every situation. A qualified team member must confirm all decisions before any override is granted or denied.</strong></div>

    <button class="reset-btn" onclick="resetAll()" style="margin:10px 0 0;width:100%;">↺ Start Over</button>

    <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--atg-teal);border-radius:0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;padding:12px 16px;margin-top:8px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:var(--atg-teal);margin-bottom:8px;">Exempt Offices</div>
