          <div class="q-label">Rare override — new carrier with specific documented reason?
            <span class="q-sub">Not high value · passes standard rules · no ownership change 365 days · cab card provided</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tog">
            <button class="tog-btn" id="nc-yes" onclick="setException('newcarrier_yes')">All Criteria Met</button>
